Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:38.68,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}The Hope and Despair of the Skeleton\Nand the Straw Hats' Counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:43.69,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Give my shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:44.86,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.22,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Moriah isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.97,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,The Sunny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.15,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Why're we back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.05,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.45,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I'm not dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.34,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I've lost my shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.70,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What a weird feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:06.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.18,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Life or death situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.85,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's no food left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.75,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The only provisions we had are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.38,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,They took all the food we've been stocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.39,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cheese and crackers are not enough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.30,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.95,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,How shameful...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.72,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:32.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I even lost my pirate lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Cheese is not enough... not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.11,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.19,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I don't see Nami-san anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:45.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,She was kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why didn't you chase her to the end of the earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.43,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.41,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,But, we were in a critical situation and we couldn't go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.37,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Who and where the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'll go save her this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:58.96,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Let me explain everything first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.90,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Listen, I'll make it short.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:08.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Right now, there are two things we must get back no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.09,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Then our shadows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:11.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That's three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.35,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's not how you're supposed to rank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.19,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,First, let me explain about Nami and the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:23.13,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Ma-!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.26,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.84,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Don't mess around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.74,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,So damn unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.27,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He sure is brave to marry Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:34.77,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,And also, I'm a giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,They made such a zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:41.43,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,So, Luffy's and the cook's zombies have been confirmed, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.74,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I never thought he was one of the Seven Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:48.39,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm scared all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.72,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.40,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If zombies resemble oneself, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I've also seen Zoro's zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.33,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.04,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He was just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:05.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He was wearing wooden clogs so, I knew it wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.01,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.67,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,If we find those three zombies and throw salt in their mouths, we'll get our shadows back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:18.12,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Anyway, good thing you found such a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:24.05,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The one who told us about their weakness and told us to come here and rescue you... was that skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You met Brook?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.28,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,And I asked him a foolish question shortly afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:39.73,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,To be honest, the first time you said he'd tag along as one of our friends, I completely disagreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:46.11,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,The more I talked with that clattering skeleton, I realized he really has bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:48.41,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Although he's a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:50.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,He's a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:52.24,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:57.29,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,While we're still at it, just answer me one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:04.15,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,If you go out in public with that look of yours, you know how people will react, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.40,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,You're a talking skeleton, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:11.08,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,There's no way someone will befriend a guy with such evil looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:13.29,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Hideous things always get despised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.93,Flashbacks,Robin,0,0,0,,Franky, what're you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:21.53,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Even if you manage to escape this cursed sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.24,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,You're aware of your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.46,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Decades of despair, unable to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.07,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,You said you were so lonely you wished to die, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:36.41,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd no longer cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.87,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Having such insignificant existence and acting all chivalrous all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.84,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Just tell us what're you hiding already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.80,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,To go that far... what do you want to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:52.18,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,What is that promise you made to your friends that you talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.10,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,You're a very nosy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.44,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:04.74,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Long ago, our pirate crew left one of our friends behind at a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.15,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,It was a very painful farewell, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:13.15,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,As our ship departed, we promised we'd return no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.87,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Then, we were annihilated on this sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.78,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,In order to not leave our promise unfulfilled....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:24.73,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,As the only member of the crew who has lived long enough, I have the duty to inform him of these events.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.73,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Since the day of our deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.76,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,It's been 50 years I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.32,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,50 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:38.10,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey! That was too long ago! I wasn't even born yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:42.35,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Sorry to say but, there's no way that guy could've waited such a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.32,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Why would he wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:48.61,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,He has the right to leave and not be kept waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:55.09,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,If by any chance he believed in our promise and has been waiting this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:59.02,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I can't imagine how lonely he must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:05.37,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,If he's been waiting this whole time while thinking we betrayed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:08.27,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I can't imagine how miserable he must feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.21,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.01,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,The name of the friend to whom we swore to meet again on that cape is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.39,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Laboon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:22.30,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,We couldn't take a little whale on our dangerous journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.22,Flashbacks,Pirates,0,0,0,,Take care, Laboon! {I cant understand this so i kinda randomly timed it.. check it please-campa}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:31.15,Flashbacks,Pirates,0,0,0,,We'll definitely come back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:39.76,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I suppose he must've grown a lot by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.33,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Is your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.50,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,A whale...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.42,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:51.54,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I can't help but think he has believed in us since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:57.42,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,He might be thinking that we'd play our cheerful music as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.50,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,And return for him with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:08.48,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I cannot ask for forgiveness after we died so irresponsibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:13.99,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,I cannot call him from the afterlife, after our reckless promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.29,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Dying is not an excuse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:26.54,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,Because a man once said that they would return no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.59,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.80,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.18,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.11,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We've met...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,that whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.58,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.39,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.04,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.51,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The Twin Capes located at the entrance of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.61,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,That's where we met that huge whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:25.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It kept bumping it's head against the Red Line, the wall which divides the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:32.78,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,For 50 years, it waited for its pirate friends who promised to return after doing a lap around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:48.09,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Somehow, Luffy stopped its suicidal habit of hitting itself against that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It still lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,And keeps waiting for its friends at those capes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.61,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What an amazing story...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:11:00.05,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Both of them have kept the promise they made 50 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:05.10,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,So, one of the friends Laboon has been waiting for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.87,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.33,Main,Ryuma,0,0,0,,If you became stronger in these past 5 years...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.93,Main,Ryuma,0,0,0,,I have as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.99,Main,Ryuma,0,0,0,,That's because our thoughts are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.80,Main,Ryuma,0,0,0,,As always, you keep treasuring that afro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.60,Main,Ryuuma,0,0,0,,You won't be able to protect such a huge weak point forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.31,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.52,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:58.23,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Do you still remember us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.04,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Whenever I think of how you must feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.82,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,It makes my heart ache...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.83,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Although I don't have a heart now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:14.81,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,We were unable to overcome the challenges of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:20.67,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Our friends have all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.67,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,As for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.08,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Not only have I lost my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:33.88,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,My face, my body... I've lost everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:35.29,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,If we ever meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:39.77,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,You won't recognize me in the skeleton shape I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.68,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Not the afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:04.42,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,I have nothing left, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:12.58,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,At least... I have this head that looks like Laboon which amused everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.08,Flashbacks,Pirate,0,0,0,,Are you brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.28,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,I'll protect it with my life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.07,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,And we'll definitely meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:29.85,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Please wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.10,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,At the promised...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.54,Thoughts,Brook,0,0,0,,Capes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Now I love both the skeleton and the whale, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.90,Main,All,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Now I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.07,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's a musician...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.86,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,A talking skeleton...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.45,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Has an afro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.31,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That Yohoho thing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.19,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,And he's Laboon's friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Even if I have to drag him, I'll make him board this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll make him our crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Do you have any objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.45,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Would you change your mind even if we had any?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:13.10,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I really want him to see Laboon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.50,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Completely agreed, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.37,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Me too, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.75,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm no longer afraid of skeletons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.98,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Now that we're fully aware of the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:26.76,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'll personally go prevent Nami-san from getting married!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.87,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.97,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Let's get going already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.68,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,We gotta recover an extra shadow now, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:43.96,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Men, get ready to counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We're pulverizing Thriller Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.03,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.61,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You're coming too, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:59.50,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Anyway, it won't be easy to find the zombies that have our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:00.42,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.28,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Luffy's zombie is extremely huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.44,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's bigger than two giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.96,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You can't hope to beat that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We don't need to search for the zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Though, I wanna see mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.88,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:19.73,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,If we stay like this, we'll never get close to the sunlight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.89,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But, don't you remember...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.46,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The old zombie man said it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.88,Flashbacks,Old man,0,0,0,,I just saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.80,Flashbacks,Old man,0,0,0,,You're terribly strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.39,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.66,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,What request?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:36.79,Flashbacks,Old man,0,0,0,,I want you to beat a certain man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.58,Flashbacks,Old man,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:44.50,Flashbacks,Old man,0,0,0,,Despite the number of victims, if you beat him, everyone will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:48.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If we take out Gekko Moriah, everyone's shadows will return!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.97,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,H-He did say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.22,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There he goes again... right to the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:56.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If we climb those stairs, we'll find Moriah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:02.98,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:07.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll go kick Gekko Moriah's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.08,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Since that'll bring everyone's shadows back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.01,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Sanji, I'll leave Nami up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.76,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.42,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I don't care whether he is an invisible man or a ceramic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.39,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'll kick the hell out of him right through the other side of this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.08,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Like I'd let that wedding take place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:31.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot to mention it, but that invisible man saw Nami completely naked in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.63,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.30,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.95,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Don't keep angering him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.02,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,He might transform into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:46.98,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I feel guilty for letting Nami get kidnapped right before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:50.05,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I'll go with Sanji too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.82,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,But mostly it's because I don't wanna come across that Warlord again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.08,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,That skeleton's fight worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.51,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,If Straw Hat beats Moriah first, that'd solve one problem but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.50,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Until that happens, getting killed by his own shadow is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:08.06,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I'll accompany you there, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:12.67,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,I'm curious about how strong this so called "Legendary Samurai" zombie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.86,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Nami-chan and Skeleton-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:18.01,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,For the time being they're our priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:22.18,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,After that, defeating Moriah is definitely the key to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.45,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.31,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Our enemy is one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.70,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.29,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Crocodile was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.19,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.45,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You were nearly killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I beg of you, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:42.65,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Especially since... I know I already said it, but your zombie is terribly huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.96,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Then, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.21,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Carry one bag at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's my Special Zombie-Purifying Salt Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.71,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ah, so this is what you were making a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.95,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.69,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:01.39,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I've got a word of advice for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.85,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,No matter how thick the fog is within this sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.52,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee sunlight won't get through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We're only safe because it's midnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,In other words, when the sun arises at daybreak, that's our ultimate time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:19.12,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That goes without saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:22.22,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Reaching daybreak without tasting food is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:28.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We'll make you regret having messed with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gekko Moriah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We'll take twice the food that was stolen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.18,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Before daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,No, you see... that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.01,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I mean the limit to recover our shad-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.01,Secondary,Zoro,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:41.64,Main,All,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:48.06,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'm coming to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:43.64,Secondary,Usopp,0,0,0,,Wait a-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.32,Secondary,Usopp,0,0,0,,Do as you wish then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.38,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.42,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,So this is a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.16,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,The sea looks awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:01.03,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,But my future looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:05.51,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll become the Pirate King with this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.08,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,Where's Oars right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.21,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,He climbed to the top of the mast, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.41,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,But... but... Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:21.13,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,We can't just sit around doing nothing while such a huge zombie wanders aimlessly around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.55,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,That guy is terribly dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.84,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:26.85,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:34.31,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,Now that we have Oars, we'll be able to steal the shadows of much stronger warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:40.57,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll have Special Zombies coming one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:46.33,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,We'll need stronger marionettes it seems, Hogback.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.72,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:56.59,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,H-Hogback-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.57,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.06,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,The pirates...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.05,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hildon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:08.37,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,The three whose shadows were stolen woke up at the ship and are heading this way with their friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.14,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.56,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Those who get their shadows stolen can't wake up that quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:17.47,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,T-Their friends found a way to wake them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:20.28,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,It seems they have some connection with the Humming One!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.70,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,Perhaps, that man told them what he knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:29.39,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,All of the pirates knowing how to purify the zombies is proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.12,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,W-What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.08,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,The zombies fear the pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.41,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,Currently, they're running from place to place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.95,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,The Wild Zombies, Surprise Zombies and Soldier Zombies, couldn't lay a hand on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:47.30,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Even before the pirates knew about the salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.64,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Deploy the General Zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.65,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,They'll take care of the pirates as long as they don't swallow salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.94,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,And what the hell is Absalom doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.84,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,Well... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.50,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,His wedding is about to start right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.28,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,Most of the general zombies are in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.66,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What are those fools doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:23.68,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, he asked if Hogback-sama could give one of his belly dances at the reception in 1 hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.17,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:28.41,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,A wedding ceremony is a once in a lifetime memorial event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:30.72,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,That'd be one funny dance-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.60,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Like I'd do that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:37.58,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Cancel that wedding this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.61,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,I'm a simple zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.98,Main,Hildon,0,0,0,,I can't go against Absalom-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:47.30,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,No need to rely on that beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:53.91,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,If my ghosts weaken them, the Soldier Zombies will be more than enough to capture them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:57.33,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Don't panic just because they know the zombies' weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.60,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,I'll capture every single one of them, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:06.13,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Prepare some marionettes for the shadows of the remaining pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:08.60,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.44,Main,Perona,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kumashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.10,Main,Bearsy,0,0,0,,Right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.63,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:15.04,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,How reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:17.05,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,I expect no less from the Ghost Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:19.51,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:22.76,Main,Cindy,0,0,0,,It would be best if you learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.82,Main,Cindy,0,0,0,,From Kumashi's example.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:26.96,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:29.28,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine, Moriah-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:31.44,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:33.22,Main,Moriah,0,0,0,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:35.05,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.33,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,In any case, you won't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.98,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,I'll stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:42.75,Main,Moria,0,0,0,,Oars amuses me more right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.51,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Then, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:51.05,Main,Hogback,0,0,0,,Since Absalom isn't doing anything, I'd like to take command of just two zombies if it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:22:54.24,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:00.06,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Where's Moriah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.06,Secondary,Zombie,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.04,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Get outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.80,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Give back the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.80,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Who's the damn bastard who peeked while Nami-san was in the shower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:12.22,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:16.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It seems we won't be needing salt for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,They're rampaging with absolute fury.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:21.67,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I wonder if they even care about the shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:25.86,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,C-Commander! There are five people heading for the Dance Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,And we can't handle the two on the bridge below!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(384,122)}{\fs35}Moriah's Dance Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,374)}{\fs35}Perona's Room
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,624)}{\fs35}Wonder Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,198)}{\fs35}{\a4}Heading to\NMoriah's\NDance Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1075,532)}{\fs35}{\a4}Heading to\NPerona's\NRoom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:36.58,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,It angers me just thinking about me being caught by these weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:42.42,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,If you're so grateful that I freed you, you can start calling me "big bro" if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:42.42,Secondary,Zoro,0,0,0,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.27,0:23:44.78,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Oh no! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.24,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:51.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,If I were to be reborn, I would want to be a maggot...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.75,0:23:55.91,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I have such large eyebrows... I'm better off dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hey! Luffy, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:23:59.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:02.08,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Robin, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:04.02,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It's the ghosts doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.46,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,When you touch them, you lose your will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:09.34,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,We haven't found a countermeasure to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:12.97,Main,Zombie,0,0,0,,Alright! I got you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:14.34,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,50)}Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:21.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:25.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If they get us too, it'll be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.63,0:24:28.73,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The ghosts have almost caught up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:32.20,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No! If we all get caught, it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:34.61,Main,Oars,0,0,0,,Set sail! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.14,0:24:47.29,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:48.67,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.67,0:24:49.71,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:02.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:06.49,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,No way, that's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.49,0:25:08.34,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.34,0:25:09.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The stairs are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.30,0:25:10.48,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,W-W-What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.48,0:25:12.26,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:16.08,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,The zombies, Usopp and Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.08,0:25:19.20,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Everyone fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.20,0:25:23.80,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Leaving aside the fact that these two fell down...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.80,0:25:25.69,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.69,0:25:29.27,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Our path was suddenly blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.27,0:25:31.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What's with that wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.71,0:25:33.36,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.36,0:25:34.80,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What the hell happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.55,0:25:39.35,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.08,0:25:44.73,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,It isn't stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.22,0:25:46.85,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.14,0:25:49.69,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.29,0:25:52.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.66,0:25:55.40,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,A huge wall suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.40,0:25:57.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Idiot! That's no wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.13,0:25:59.97,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,That's Luffy's zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:01.01,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What?!
